summary: Cyrus: T.J.’s Best Friend: Established in 3x07 when T.J. stated that Cyrus was “The only one he could talk to like this”. This...
body:
Cyrus:

  • T.J.’s Best Friend: Established in 3x07 when T.J. stated that Cyrus was “The only one he could talk to like this”. This line confirms that T.J. views Cyrus as his closest and most trusted peer. Making Cyrus T.J.’s best friend.

Buffy: 

  • Cyrus’ Best Friend Since The 2nd Grade: Athletic, Stubborn, Competitive, Loyal, Defensive, Values portraying strength and hates appearing incompetent/weak, Cherishes Cyrus’ friendship greatly and feels completely at ease in his presence, Cyrus and Buffy both acknowledge each other’s faults and strengths; and are closer armed with the knowledge that neither of them are perfect.

T.J.:

summary: TJ and Cyrus’ Swing Scenes Compared It was nice of Instagram’s Tyrusbabytaters to repost my recent post comparing the two scenes...
caption:
TJ and Cyrus’ Swing Scenes Compared

It was nice of Instagram’s Tyrusbabytaters to repost my recent post comparing the two scenes of Cyrus and TJ at the swings.  However, they didn’t post both pictures, but just posted the one still photo twice.  This gave the mistaken impression that I had seen some tiny detail that was different in two obviously identical pictures.  So I am now posting the two pictures above, that will hopefully be noticed by the Instagram people, which clearly show the photo (top) and filmed scene (bottom) are different.
